<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en-US">
<head>
  <title>Brave UX - Work - B-Line Medical</title>
  <%- include ../partials/_head %>
</head>
<body>
  <main class="wrapper case-study bline">
    <header class="case-header">
      <div class="case-header-content container">
        <h5 class="case-header-client-name">B-Line Medical</h5>
        <h1 class="case-header-tagline">Take a learning tool&nbsp;<br />to the next level</h1>
        <h6 class="case-header-type">Healthcare Simulation Application</h6>
      </div>
    </header>

    <section class="case-exec-summary padded blue">
      <div class="container">
        <p class="case-exec-summary-text">We redesigned an application that manages and debriefs medical simulations for healthcare students.</p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="case-breakdown padded light-blue">
      <div class="container row between">
        <div class="case-breakdown-box column gutter">
          <p class="case-breakdown-heading">Challenge</p>
          <h3 class="case-breakdown-summary">
            Make a tool indispensable
          </h3>
          <p class="case-breakdown-detail">
            We took the bones of the application and set out to make it incredibly intuitive as well as beautiful.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="case-breakdown-box column gutter">
          <p class="case-breakdown-heading">Solution</p>
          <h3 class="case-breakdown-summary">
            Form meets function
          </h3>
          <p class="case-breakdown-detail">
            Our redesign blends modern usability with a clean look to guide users and help them with the task at hand.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="case-breakdown-box column gutter">
          <p class="case-breakdown-heading">Scope</p>
          <ul class="case-breakdown-list">
            <li class="case-breakdown-list-item">Information Architecture</li>
            <li class="case-breakdown-list-item">Application Design</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="block padded">
      <div class="row container">
        <div class="inner-block absolute-center-md gutter-bottom-mobile column half-md one-third-lg">
          <div class="inner-block-content gutter-right">
            <h2 class="case-block-heading">Fly through&nbsp;<br />management tasks</h2>
            <p class="case-block-text">
              With a prioritized column layout and page-level navigation, management is quick and easy.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="inner-block column column-block align-self-center half-md two-third-lg">
          <div class="frame frame-desktop dark shadow sr-right lazy-ratio" data-width="1464" data-height="830">
            <img data-normal="./images/work/bline/desktop-management.jpg" alt="Display of one of the pages of the website app." class="inner-block-image contain">
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="block">
      <img data-normal="./images/work/bline/hospital.jpg" alt="A hospital hallway with a group of medical students carrying notebooks peering through the glass of an interior office." class="block-image">
    </section>

    <section class="block padded blue">
      <div class="row container">
        <div class="inner-block column column-block align-self-center half-md sr-left">
          <div class="lazy-ratio" data-width="300" data-height="141">
            <img data-normal="./images/work/bline/data.svg" alt="A stylized dot graph showing data points spread across several months of the year." class="inner-block-image contain">
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="inner-block absolute-center-md order-top-xs gutter-bottom-mobile column half-md">
          <div class="inner-block-content gutter-left">
            <h2 class="case-block-heading">Data when&nbsp;<br />you need it</h2>
            <p class="case-block-text">
              A layer of detailed simulation data can be expanded when needed. When itâ€™s in the way, you can collapse it or enter theater mode to focus solely on the video itself.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="block" style="background: url(./images/work/bline/multi-data-bg.svg) #fff bottom center/contain no-repeat;">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="inner-block">
          <div class="lazy-ratio" data-width="300" data-height="165">
            <img data-normal="./images/work/bline/multi-data1.svg" alt="a card containing an example bar graph" class="inner-block-image contain sr-stagger-bottom">
            <img data-normal="./images/work/bline/multi-data2.svg" alt="a card showing an example dot graph shaded in blue" class="inner-block-image contain sr-stagger-bottom">
            <img data-normal="./images/work/bline/multi-data3.svg" alt="a card showing an example dot graph shaded in green" class="inner-block-image contain sr-stagger-bottom">
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="block padded-top gray">
      <div class="inner-block row absolute-center-md order-top-xs padded-bottom">
        <div class="inner-block-content content-centered container">
          <h2 class="case-block-heading">Provide an organized workspace</h2>
          <p class="case-block-text">
            Users have everything they need for their workflow, with annotations, data, and a multi-layout video player all in a clear and efficient structure.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="inner-block row">
        <div class="container-narrow">
          <div class="frame frame-desktop dark shadow sr-bottom lazy-ratio" data-width="1360" data-height="768">
            <img data-normal="./images/work/bline/desktop-operation.jpg" alt="a desktop display of the app showing an educational medical video and annotated timeline" class="inner-block-image contain">
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="block row">
      <div class="inner-block absolute-center-md padded column half-md light-blue">
        <div class="inner-block-content container">
          <h2 class="case-block-heading">Out with the old,&nbsp;<br />in with the new</h2>
          <p class="case-block-text">
            We designed the zero-state to be fully interactive, ensuring that users can get through each step with as little effort as possible.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="inner-block column column-block align-self-center half-md blue hide-overflow">
        <div class="lazy-ratio" data-width="146" data-height="150">
          <img data-normal="./images/work/bline/interactive1.svg" alt="an example of the basic information interface within the app" class="inner-block-image sr-left">
          <img data-normal="./images/work/bline/interactive2.svg" alt="an example of the add people to session interface within the app" class="inner-block-image sr-right">
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="block padded">
      <div class="inner-block row">
        <div class="container-narrow">
          <div class="lazy-ratio" data-width="261" data-height="150">
            <img data-normal="./images/work/bline/icons.svg" alt="a card containing an example bar graph" class="inner-block-image contain sr-bottom">
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="case-referral row">
      <div class="inner-block padded column absolute-center-xs half-md blue">
        <div class="container">
          <p class="case-referral-blockquote">Brave helped us completely rethink the UX of our platform</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="inner-block padded column half-md gray">
        <div class="container">
          <div class="case-referral-quote-icon"></div>
          <p class="case-referral-text">Brave helped us completely rethink the UX of our platform, asking questions and making us step outside our own and into our users&rsquo; mindset. Working with Brave not only improved our platform, but how we think about UX.</p>
          <p class="case-referral-author">Chafic Kazoun, <em>Co-Founder and Chairman, B-Line Medical</em></p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>

  <%- include ../partials/_footer-scripts %>
  
</body>
</html>
